Adjustments Explained:
position: sticky; top: 0;: This style will keep your "Product Sort:" label and the dropdown at the top of the viewport when you scroll. Adjust the top value based on your layout needs.
background: "white": Adding a background to the sticky element prevents any content below it from showing through. This can help in maintaining a clean UI.
zIndex: 1000: Ensures that your sticky header stays on top of other content as you scroll.
marginLeft: "8px": Optionally, this will add space between the label and the dropdown, making it visually appealing.
